<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased API Error Rates>
Between 11:01 AM and 11:20 AM PDT we experienced increased error rates in creating and accessing Cloud9 environments in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
We are investigating increased error rates and latencies for the IAM APIs.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
Between 3:38 PM and 4:11 PM PDT we experienced increased IAM API error rates and latencies. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
